{"tid":2044020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美港警暴問題，最大分別係個制衡機制","createTime":"2020-05-30T21:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T00:56:56.000Z","uid":50457,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b31c7f095cbb6f6d62df77a7c484cfbccc52efa","tid":2044020,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:03:30.000Z","msg":"香港係無制衡機制，根本就唔係如何警暴，如何示威的問題。<br />\n<br />\n示威同警暴，一直以來都有，邊度都係，重點係有無機制制衡兩邊，而唔會失去平衡。<br />\n<br />\n民主制度的可貴，在於約束政府權力的機制, 只有政府權力被約束，先可以穩定國家。<br />\n<br />\n盲目強調衝突畫面，只係五毛轉移視線的技巧。講真，呢類種族衝突幾年就一次，根本係尋常事。"},{"pid":"c6a89adf4ee803ccaf53bf6b71f77e00010c5e43","tid":2044020,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T22:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6cc5dc49f769946cef662cf6b3be50c3449f43","tid":2044020,"uid":87377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T22:50:05.000Z","msg":"香港黑警 委任證都冇張"},{"pid":"cd3a9e8d0f2ba986de7d6cc6b370b19935d8d8d9","tid":2044020,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T22:51:22.000Z","msg":"無錯, 屌鳩藍屍用一句殺人黑警已被控謀殺就搞掂"},{"pid":"d8f92a40c96ef66886ccbbb978c44597dc8b324e","tid":2044020,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T23:12:12.000Z","msg":"班友算把啦⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個風係唔會吹得起<br />\n美國點處理全世界有眼睇<br />\n問責既問責<br />\n調查既調查<br />\n可以撩到d乜<br />\n<br />\n相反越反映到港警暴個種荒謬<br />\n冇人問責，冇調查"},{"pid":"9f0c5751134cadd909d9c385a6d9e6974143fc6d","tid":2044020,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f92a40c96ef66886ccbbb978c44597dc8b324e","tid":2044020,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T23:12:12.000Z","msg":"班友算把啦⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj